# Napkin: Always Active

At session start, read `.agent/memory/distilled.md` then `.agent/memory/napkin.md` (if they exist). If `napkin.md` does not exist, create it with a session heading.

Write to the napkin as you work: mistakes you make, corrections the user gives you, surprises, patterns that work or don't. See `.cursor/skills/napkin/SKILL.md` for full guidance.
